OAuth - Open Authorization Standard or framework which delegates Authorization
       to third party application for limited access of webservice or http resources.

Authentication - OpenID connect

Terminology
   Resource Owner - user
   Client App  ~ bookmyshow website
   Resource Server   ~ Google / Facebook
   Authorization Server  ~ Google / Facebook
Client Id -
    Agreement between client app and oAuth provider
     - Client id and Secret
Grant Types
  Authorization Code


  Implicit
  Resource password credentials
  Client password credentials


  Assignment
   - Automate following twitter APIs in restAssured
     - Get Timeline
     - Post Tweet
     - Search user
     - User Timeline
Validate ANY 4 APIs and validate minimum 4 fields for every API
